PAGE 24: The End
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thank you for reading this story of unfailing love. May it remind you of the 
depth of God's love for each of us, a love that pursues, redeems, and restores.

"For God so loved the world that he gave his one and only Son, that whoever 
believes in him shall not perish but have eternal life."
— John 3:16


